</fr>
</cm>
<cm>
<sv num="10" id="Mateo-19-10"/>
His disciples said to him, «If this is the case of the man with his
wife, it is not expedient to marry.»  
<t lang="es">Sus discípulos le dijeron, «</t>
<rb lang="es">Si tal es la dificultad entre marido y esposa, no vale la
